				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">When a heroic opportunity begins there will be a coin in the corner:
<br />

<br />
<img src="http://images.crgaming.com/7200.jpg" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
If you use a spell with a coin icon, it will pick an HO randomly from that same trigger chain - it might be the same one. Lists of all the HOs for each trigger chain (usually 2 regular ones and 1 rare one) are in the HO section of the site.[/img]</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
