				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Basic Rules for HO's:
<br />

<br />
- Everyone fights using basic attacks only.  No special attacks means no broken HO's.
<br />
- The starter MUST announce the HO is inbound using a macro, "&lt;&lt;&lt; Inc HO, 5 seconds &gt;&gt;&gt;".
<br />

<br />
I had a pickup group that hit 5-6 HO's every fight.  Just takes coordination and patience.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
